SIMPLE: unanswered
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unanswered
<hw>Unanswered</hw> <def>See <er>answered</er>.</def>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unanswered
<hw>Un*an"swered</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
answered; not replied to; <as>as, an <ex>unanswered</ex>
letter</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not refuted; <as>as, an <ex>unanswered</ex>
argument</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not responded to in kind; unrequited; <as>as,
<ex>unanswered</ex> affection</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unappalled</ent>⟦br⟧
